sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Utilisateur
    participant ALB as Load Balancer
    participant API as Django API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant FCM as Firebase FCM

    U->>ALB: POST /api/transaction/send-money/ (JWT Bearer)
    ALB->>API: Forward — HTTPS TLS 1.3
    API->>API: Validation JWT · Rate limit · Resolve destinataire
    API->>DB: Vérification solde (WalletBalanceHistory)
    DB-->>API: Solde suffisant ✓
    API->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION SERIALIZABLE
    API->>DB: INSERT Transaction (status=PENDING)
    API->>DB: DEBIT wallet expéditeur + INSERT History
    API->>DB: CREDIT wallet destinataire + INSERT History
    API->>DB: DEBIT frais → wallet PLIIIZ + INSERT FeeDistribution
    API->>DB: UPDATE Transaction (status=SUCCESS)
    API->>DB: COMMIT
    DB-->>API: OK ✓
    API->>FCM: Push notification expéditeur
    API->>FCM: Push notification destinataire
    API-->>U: 200 OK · order_id · status: success